FT  20 MAY 94 / UK Company News: Crown Products for market
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Crown Products Group, which consists of Crown Toys &amp; Gifts and which
proposes to acquire Children Design &amp; Leisure, is seeking to gain a listing
under Stock Exchange Rule 535.2 from May 27.
