<HEADLINE>
FT  20 MAY 94 / UK reply to Sinn Fein welcomed by Dublin
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By DAVID OWEN and TIM COONE
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   LONDON, DUBLIN
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
The UK government last night called on Irish republican leaders to halt the
