FT  19 MAY 94 / Observer: Facts found
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Is the video age catching up with Westminster at last? Having put up with
and/or taken starring roles in front of the television cameras in the House
for some years now, MPs may be less than thrilled by the emergence of the
